OL,3,CCouncil's plan to replace Victorian
OL,4,Clampposts 'not appropriate',
OL,5,Ccampaigners say
OL,7,FProposed plans to replace Victorian
OL,8,Fcast iron lampposts in Canterbury have
OL,9,Fbeen met with anger from those
OL,10,Fpassionate about preserving the city's
OL,11,Fheritage.
OL,13,FThere are 293 of these ornate
OL,14,Flampposts across the city and were
OL,15,Fsome of the first electric
OL,16,Fstreetlights seen in Britain.
