OL,3,CCouncil's plan to replace Victorian
OL,4,Clampposts 'not appropriate',
OL,5,Ccampaigners say
OL,7,FKent County Council says recent safety
OL,8,Finspections have revealed 'serious
OL,9,Fstructural issues' and so plans have
OL,10,Fbeen proposed to replace them with
OL,11,Fmodern, steel lampposts.
OL,13,FHowever historian's say this will be
OL,14,F'tragic' for the area.
OL,16,FGuy Mayhew from The Canterbury Society
OL,17,Fsaid: "They surround the city's
OL,18,Fhistoric core, ranging from different
OL,19,Feras and different years. Some of them
OL,20,Fdate back to the early 1900s.
