OL,3,CCouncil's plan to replace Victorian
OL,4,Clampposts 'not appropriate',
OL,5,Ccampaigners say
OL,7,F"Some of them are in a poor state of
OL,8,Frepair, but the idea to wholesale
OL,9,Fremove them is quite tragic really."
OL,11,FHe added: "Taking an off-the-shelf
OL,12,Fsolution and plastering that over a
OL,13,Fworld heritage site is not appropriate.
OL,15,F"It doesn't respect Canterbury's
OL,16,Fheritage."
