OL,3,CCouncil's plan to replace Victorian
OL,4,Clampposts 'not appropriate',
OL,5,Ccampaigners say
OL,7,FThe county council says that to
OL,8,Freplace or repair the Victorian
OL,9,Flampposts would cost around #5,000
OL,10,Feach which would eat into the 'limited
OL,11,Fmaintenance budget', compared to the
OL,12,Fmodern lampposts costing #810 each.
OL,14,FIt added that the existing ornate
OL,15,Flanterns would instead be re-used to
OL,16,F'maintain the character of
OL,17,FCanterbury's streets'.
