OL,3,CCouncil's plan to replace Victorian
OL,4,Clampposts 'not appropriate',
OL,5,Ccampaigners say
OL,7,FA spokesperson from Kent County
OL,8,FCouncil (KCC) said: "These are
OL,9,Fproposed works which have not yet
OL,10,Fstarted. We have been working closely
OL,11,Fwith Canterbury City Council to find a
OL,12,Fsolution and move this work forward.
OL,14,F"The Canterbury Society has not
OL,15,Fcontacted us to discuss these plans.
OL,17,F"We understand the historic
OL,18,Fsignificance of the Biggleston
OL,19,Flampposts in Canterbury and the
OL,20,Faffection residents have for them.
