OL,3,CCouncil's plan to replace Victorian
OL,4,Clampposts 'not appropriate',
OL,5,Ccampaigners say
OL,7,F"The cast iron columns have failed
OL,8,Fstructural tests carried out at the
OL,9,Fbase of the column, confirming
OL,10,Finternal corrosion and other defects.
OL,11,FPainting the columns would only
OL,12,Fprotect the part above ground and does
OL,13,Fnot address the damage inside or
OL,14,Funderground.
OL,16,F"The original factory that produced
OL,17,Fthese lampposts has closed, and the
OL,18,Fmoulds used to make them no longer
OL,19,Fexist.
