OL,3,CCouncil's plan to replace Victorian
OL,4,Clampposts 'not appropriate',
OL,5,Ccampaigners say
OL,7,F"It is anticipated that creating a
OL,8,Fbespoke mould alone would cost tens of
OL,9,Fthousands of pounds, and each new cast
OL,10,Firon column could cost in excess of
OL,11,F#5,000.
OL,13,F'By comparison, installing a modern
OL,14,Fsteel lamppost costs about #168, and
OL,15,Fadding a heritage-style decorative kit
OL,16,Fbrings the total to around #810 per
OL,17,Flamppost. These kits are made from
OL,18,Fdurable, non-metal materials, which
OL,19,Fmakes future safety checks easier,
OL,20,Fsafer, and more cost-effective.
