OL,3,CCouncil's plan to replace Victorian
OL,4,Clampposts 'not appropriate',
OL,5,Ccampaigners say
OL,7,F"While we appreciate the historic
OL,8,Fvalue of the Biggleston lampposts,
OL,9,Fpublic safety must come first. Our
OL,10,Fapproach ensures that Canterbury
OL,11,Fretains a heritage look while meeting
OL,12,Fmodern safety standards."
